If I eat fried chicken, I’ll only eat 2 pieces instead of 4. No fries. Steak no sides. Still can’t stop soda too long but I’m tryna (not really but still) I only drink soda when I’m out eating. Inside it’s water for me. If I get a burger or Poboy, I only eat half. Imma start exercising when I go back home. I don’t want lose too fast and have flabby inside thighs like I did when I was sick lmao. My shit looked like a wrinkle titties between my legs lmao. But yea.. you get the point. Shop with @shopboujeehippie
